<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" class="thumbnail" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/othree/8663489278/" title="和服少女 by othree, on Flickr"><img src="https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8246/8663489278_2d74217319_b.jpg" width="683" height="1024" alt="和服少女" srcset="https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8246/8663489278_2d74217319_b.jpg 683w, https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8246/8663489278_e75a356a87_h.jpg 1067w" /></a></p>

