<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" class="thumbnail" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/othree/8664862855/" title="清水寺 櫻花 by othree, on Flickr"><img src="https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8249/8664862855_e3e2c3e664_b.jpg" width="683" height="1024" alt="清水寺 櫻花" srcset="https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8249/8664862855_e3e2c3e664_b.jpg 683w, https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8249/8664862855_419dc93620_h.jpg 1067w" /></a></p>

